metadata.name: Lucky Lightning Rain
metadata.description:
Raining electric luck from above.  
Z Lucky Corporation is the ZEconomy leader in all kinds of luck value in life. 

PubliZity uses advertising to promote possible narratives of living life. Each poster promotes a happening of living and is meant to emphasize consuming the value of living our quotidian instead of objects. 
Advertising with the goal of keeping us grounded in the moment instead of promoting the next mindless distraction.

Z Lucky Corporation is a JaZoN Ex.* Listed Company. 
 
 www.jazonex.com/zlucky

*JaZoN Ex. redefines portraiture, self worth, and the value of an individual in the form of a stock market. Composed of companies that valorize living in all its forms: experiences, intellect, sexuality, physical health, emotions… etc, the oeuvre is a multi faceted, continually evolving accumulation and implementation of data generated by JaZoN’s interpretation of life. Featuring multiple hundreds of thousands of price evaluations to date, the global project is expressed in both virtual and physical forms going all the way back to 2007.
